{"id":217066,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/03/维权网-推友称因响应唯色发起的签名，账号遭到/","date":"2012-03-23T15:08:01Z","modified":"2012-03-23T15:08:01Z","title":"维权网 | 推友称因响应唯色发起的签名，账号遭到推特官方冻结（图）","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" name=\"more\"></a>（维权网信息员刘彤报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span><span>日下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>点</span><span>左右，国内一位活跃的推特号为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">@444284325</span><span>推友致电本网信息员称：他的推特账号被推特官方给冻结了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">!</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>信息员闻讯感到惊奇，国内微薄账号被冻结是常有的事情</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>而推特官方网站上账号被冻结，笔者还是第一次听说，于是就此对其进行了采访，以下是采访记录</span><span> <span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span></span><span>为保障对方安全暂不公布其电话和姓名，如需采访请联系本网站</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span><span>。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>信息员</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">:</span><span>你是通过什么方式上推特网</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">?</span></div>\n<div><span>推友</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">:</span><span>我是用自由门直接上的推特官方网址</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">:twitter.com.</span></div>\n<div><span>信息员</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">:</span><span>奇怪了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>那么你最近一段时间都发了一些什么内容你认为可能会比较敏感呢</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">?</span></div>\n<div><span>推友</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">:</span><span>我在推特上主要说了些藏民的事情</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>也没有其他什么</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span></div>\n<div><span>信息员：那么你最后一次正常上推特是什么时候？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>推友：大约</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日晚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>点</span><span>左右。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>信息员：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日</span><span>当天你说了些什么？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>推友：主要是发了些支持藏族作家唯色在她自己博客上发起的：《吁请藏人再勿自焚：压迫再大也要留住生命</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://woeser.middle-way.net/2012/03/3284.html\">http://woeser.middle-way.net/2012/03/3284.html</a></span><span>》签名活动。结果第二天却发现账号被冻结了。</span></div>\n<div><span>信息员：你什么时候发现不能登录推特账号的？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>推友：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">21</span><span>日</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>分</span><span>左右</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>信息员：页面显示什么？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>推友：网页提示：你的账号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">@444284325</span><span>已被冻结，更多信息，请访问（已冻结的账号），可我点击此处却无法打开。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>信息员：能否将你的网页做个截图给我？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>推友：对不起我不会，我可以给你密码，你自己登录看看。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>信息员：谢谢！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>信息员打开页面后发现：除了这位推友描述的情况外，这个账号的所有关注者和被关注者都为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">0</span><span>了，而发的推文总共</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">753</span><span>条却还保留在账号中。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>本周以来，很多拥有推特账号的大陆用户，都发现了推特的异常现象。比如本来已经加为关注的推友，却自动消失，并有多人发现</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">FO</span><span>的数量一天内无故少了数十人。但推特账号被直接冻结，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">@444284325</span><span>推友恐怕还是第一个。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>网页截图：如需验证，请联系维权网。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-MhJarSPXqhs/T2ss8V9RFiI/AAAAAAAAF_Y/zpJJs-u2h68/s1600/%E7%BD%91%E9%A1%B51111111111111111.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-MhJarSPXqhs/T2ss8V9RFiI/AAAAAAAAF_Y/zpJJs-u2h68/s320/%E7%BD%91%E9%A1%B51111111111111111.jpg\" width=\"317\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-skgg8Ez2zXg/T2ss_elXRiI/AAAAAAAAF_g/PKVlEiCIW-4/s1600/%E7%BD%91%E9%A1%B5222222.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"216\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-skgg8Ez2zXg/T2ss_elXRiI/AAAAAAAAF_g/PKVlEiCIW-4/s320/%E7%BD%91%E9%A1%B5222222.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img alt=\"\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-1632397667383502793?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" width=\"1\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=738338\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"738338\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/embeddedform?formkey=dGRpN3FrVThuMFFsZHBZcmNGLW94dEE6MQ\" width=\"450\" height=\"309\" frameborder=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\">Loading&#8230;</iframe></p>\n","author":1004,"categories":[20534],"tags":[5908,8339,8951,8604,8795]}